# Vue and Nuxt UI

- Prefer `@nuxt/ui` components where they fit. Use composables from `@vueuse/core` and from project `app/composables/` when relevant.
- Use Tailwind for styling. Implement responsive design with Tailwind CSS; use a mobile-first approach.
